{% comment %}
  HARAMOON Complete 4-Step Glass Skin Routine Page
  Structure: Problem → Agitate → Solution (PAS) + 4 routine steps + ingredients + bundle CTA
  Uses: haramoon_101 metaobject entries (one per step), ingredient_profile metaobject references
{% endcomment %}

{%- assign hm_steps = shop.metaobjects.haramoon_101.values -%}
{%- assign sorted_steps = hm_steps | sort: 'routine_step_number' -%}

<div class="hm-routine-page" id="haramoon-routine">

  {%- comment -%} ── SECTION 1: MULTIVITAMIN PHILOSOPHY ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="hm-manifesto hm-manifesto--multivitamin" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Article">
    <div class="hm-manifesto__inner">
      <p class="hm-routine-eyebrow">The HARAMOON Philosophy</p>
      <h2 class="hm-manifesto__title" itemprop="headline">Think of HARAMOON as a Multivitamin For Your Skin.</h2>
      <div class="hm-manifesto__body" itemprop="description">
        <p>It&rsquo;s not a full buffet of trendy, targeted treatments. It&rsquo;s not a sugary dessert. It is the fundamental, foundational nutrition your skin has been craving &mdash; a reliable, easy, and science-backed system that delivers noticeable results, fast. HARAMOON functions like a multivitamin for skin: essential support for barrier health, hydration, and balance.</p>
        <p>Skincare works like nutrition. Just as fruits, vegetables, and whole foods sustain your health, barrier care and hydration sustain your skin. Treatments and brighteners are the occasional extras &mdash; not the core meal.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hm-manifesto__two-col">
        <div class="hm-manifesto__col">
          <h3 class="hm-manifesto__col-title">Changes You&rsquo;ll Notice First</h3>
          <p class="hm-manifesto__col-sub">(How you know your barrier is getting stronger)</p>
          <ul class="hm-manifesto__list">
            <li><strong>Less tightness after cleansing.</strong> Your skin feels clean, but comfortable.</li>
            <li><strong>Makeup sits better.</strong> It glides on smoothly and stays fresh all day.</li>
            <li><strong>Pores appear smaller</strong> at the end of the day, less stretched and congested.</li>
            <li><strong>Blemishes heal faster.</strong> Zits that surface come to a head and resolve without a fight.</li>
            <li><strong>Redness visibly reduces.</strong> A new sense of calm and evenness across your skin.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="hm-manifesto__col">
          <h3 class="hm-manifesto__col-title">The Long Game</h3>
          <p class="hm-manifesto__col-sub">(What happens when you stay consistent)</p>
          <ul class="hm-manifesto__list">
            <li><strong>Overall color correction.</strong> A more even, luminous skin tone over time.</li>
            <li><strong>Those forever blackheads on your nose?</strong> They slowly but surely disintegrate.</li>
            <li><strong>Fewer ingrown hairs</strong> from waxing or plucking.</li>
            <li><strong>No new fine lines setting in.</strong> HARAMOON deters premature aging &mdash; it doesn&rsquo;t just claim to.</li>
            <li><strong>Zits that surface actually heal.</strong> No more endless underground blemishes.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hm-manifesto__synergy">
        <p class="hm-manifesto__synergy-text">You&rsquo;ll notice a difference with just <strong>one HARAMOON product</strong>. But their formulas are engineered to work in synergy. The more of the four steps you use, the faster the changes come &mdash; and the clearer it becomes which skincare products actually work for you, and which are just noise.</p>
        <blockquote class="hm-manifesto__quote">&ldquo;Why layer 12 products when one actually works? HARAMOON &gt; the drugstore aisle.&rdquo;</blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── SECTION 2: K-BEAUTY TRUTH ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="hm-manifesto hm-manifesto--kbeauty" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Article">
    <div class="hm-manifesto__inner">
      <p class="hm-routine-eyebrow">You Don&rsquo;t Need More Products. You Need The Right Ones.</p>
      <h2 class="hm-manifesto__title" itemprop="headline">It&rsquo;s Not Your Fault. It&rsquo;s Your Skincare.</h2>
      <div class="hm-manifesto__body" itemprop="description">
        <p>You&rsquo;re no newbie to skincare brands claiming the latest ingredient or trend is the holy grail. You read skincare labels because you&rsquo;ve discovered at least one or two ingredients that consistently act as your skin&rsquo;s nemesis &mdash; and you won&rsquo;t ever voluntarily allow that ish to touch your face again.</p>
        <p><strong>It&rsquo;s not your fault. Western brands are built based on their revenue. Korean brands are built based on their function.</strong></p>
        <p>Expect HARAMOON to be different than anything you&rsquo;ve tried before, because it is. Available exclusively in the USA right here at Wax &amp; Wane.</p>
        <p>Most Western skincare is designed to mask problems, not solve them. &ldquo;Western brands treat problems. Korean skincare prevents them.&rdquo; And much of the &ldquo;K-beauty&rdquo; you see in major retailers is a watered-down version, formulated for mass appeal rather than maximum potency &mdash; less motive to skim off the top for quality when your business is volume, not results.</p>
        <p>Real Korean skincare is a different ballgame. It&rsquo;s a philosophy built on a simple, powerful idea: <strong>skin health is earned, not masked.</strong> It&rsquo;s about building a foundation so strong that your skin can finally breathe, heal, and thrive on its own.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hm-manifesto__quote-grid">
        <blockquote class="hm-manifesto__quote-card">&ldquo;Conventional skincare = yesterday&rsquo;s news. K-Beauty = next-gen glow.&rdquo;</blockquote>
        <blockquote class="hm-manifesto__quote-card">&ldquo;Old routine: strip + repair. New routine: protect + strengthen.&rdquo;</blockquote>
        <blockquote class="hm-manifesto__quote-card">&ldquo;Less filler, more function &mdash; because your skin deserves more than marketing fluff.&rdquo;</blockquote>
        <blockquote class="hm-manifesto__quote-card">&ldquo;Stop fighting your skin. Start feeding it.&rdquo;</blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── HERO / PAS PROBLEM ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="hm-routine-hero">
    <div class="hm-routine-hero__inner">
      <p class="hm-routine-eyebrow">{{ section.settings.eyebrow | default: 'HARAMOON × Korean Glass Skin' }}</p>
      <h1 class="hm-routine-hero__title">{{ section.settings.hero_title | default: 'Your Skin Has Been Trying to Tell You Something.' }}</h1>
      <p class="hm-routine-hero__problem">{{ section.settings.problem_text | default: 'Dullness. Uneven texture. Products that promise everything and deliver nothing. You have tried the 10-step routines, the trending serums, the overnight miracles. And your skin is still not where you want it to be.' }}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── AGITATE ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="hm-routine-agitate">
    <div class="hm-routine-agitate__inner">
      <h2 class="hm-routine-agitate__title">{{ section.settings.agitate_title | default: 'The Problem Is Not Your Skin. It Is Your Routine.' }}</h2>
      <p class="hm-routine-agitate__body">{{ section.settings.agitate_text | default: 'Most Western skincare is formulated to mask, not transform. Korean skincare is different. It is built on the principle that skin health is earned through consistency, layering, and ingredients that work with your biology. HARAMOON distills decades of K-beauty science into precise steps. No filler. No fluff. Just glass skin.' }}</p>
      <div class="hm-routine-agitate__stats">
        <div class="hm-routine-stat">
          <span class="hm-routine-stat__number">4</span>
          <span class="hm-routine-stat__label">Steps</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hm-routine-stat">
          <span class="hm-routine-stat__number">~5</span>
          <span class="hm-routine-stat__label">Minutes</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hm-routine-stat">
          <span class="hm-routine-stat__number">AM + PM</span>
          <span class="hm-routine-stat__label">Daily</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hm-routine-stat">
          <span class="hm-routine-stat__number">14</span>
          <span class="hm-routine-stat__label">Days to Visible Results</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── SOLUTION: THE 4 STEPS ── {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="hm-routine-steps-section">
    <div class="hm-routine-steps-section__inner">
      <p class="hm-routine-eyebrow">The Solution</p>
      <h2 class="hm-routine-steps-section__title">{{ section.settings.steps_title | default: 'The HARAMOON 4-Step Glass Skin System' }}</h2>
      <p class="hm-routine-steps-section__subtitle">{{ section.settings.steps_subtitle | default: 'Each step is engineered to work with the next. Skip one and you break the chain.' }}</p>

      {%- comment -%} Step progress indicator {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="hm-routine-progress" aria-label="Routine steps">
        {%- for i in (1..4) -%}
          <div class="hm-routine-progress__item">
            <div class="hm-routine-progress__circle">{{ i }}</div>
            {%- if i < 4 -%}<div class="hm-routine-progress__line"></div>{%- endif -%}
          </div>
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>

      {%- comment -%} Step cards — pulled from haramoon_101 metaobject {%- endcomment -%}
      <div class="hm-routine-steps-grid">
        {%- if sorted_steps.size > 0 -%}
          {%- for step in sorted_steps -%}
            {%- assign step_num = step.routine_step_number | default: forloop.index -%}
            {%- assign step_name = step.routine_step_name | default: step.product_name_type -%}
            {%- assign step_claims = step.key_claims -%}
            {%- assign step_story = step.product_story -%}
            {%- assign step_benefits = step.skin_care_benefits -%}
            {%- assign step_clinical = step.clinical_results -%}
            {%- assign step_ingredients = step.ingredient_profile -%}
            <div class="hm-routine-step-card" data-step="{{ step_num }}">
              <div class="hm-routine-step-card__header">
                <span class="hm-routine-step-card__number">Step {{ step_num }}</span>
                <h3 class="hm-routine-step-card__name">{{ step_name }}</h3>
                {%- if step.product_highlight != blank -%}
                  <p class="hm-routine-step-card__highlight">{{ step.product_highlight }}</p>
                {%- endif -%}
              </div>

              {%- comment -%} Product image if available {%- endcomment -%}
              {%- if step.images and step.images.size > 0 -%}
                <div class="hm-routine-step-card__image">
                  {{ step.images.first | image_url: width: 600 | image_tag: alt: step_name, loading: 'lazy' }}
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}

              <div class="hm-routine-step-card__body">
                {%- if step_story != blank -%}
                  <p class="hm-routine-step-card__story">{{ step_story }}</p>
                {%- endif -%}

                {%- if step_claims and step_claims.size > 0 -%}
                  <ul class="hm-routine-step-card__claims">
                    {%- for claim in step_claims -%}
                      <li>{{ claim }}</li>
                    {%- endfor -%}
                  </ul>
                {%- endif -%}

                {%- if step_benefits != blank -%}
                  <div class="hm-routine-step-card__benefits">
                    <span class="hm-routine-step-card__label">Skin Benefits</span>
                    <p>{{ step_benefits }}</p>
                  </div>
                {%- endif -%}

                {%- if step_clinical != blank -%}
                  <div class="hm-routine-step-card__clinical">
                    <span class="hm-routine-step-card__label">Clinical Results</span>
                    <div class="hm-routine-step-card__clinical-body rte">{{ step_clinical | metafield_tag }}</div>
                  </div>
                {%- endif -%}

                {%- comment -%} Linked ingredient profiles {%- endcomment -%}
                {%- if step_ingredients and step_ingredients.size > 0 -%}
                  <div class="hm-routine-step-card__ingredients">
                    <span class="hm-routine-step-card__label">Key Ingredients</span>
                    <div class="hm-routine-ingredient-chips">
                      {%- for ing in step_ingredients -%}
                        {%- assign ing_obj = ing.value -%}
                        {%- assign ing_name = ing_obj.ingredient_name | default: ing_obj.name -%}
                        {%- if ing_obj.system.url != blank -%}
                          <a href="{{ ing_obj.system.url }}" class="hm-routine-ingredient-chip hm-routine-ingredient-chip--link">{{ ing_name }}</a>
                        {%- else -%}
                          <span class="hm-routine-ingredient-chip">{{ ing_name }}</span>
                        {%- endif -%}
                      {%- endfor -%}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                {%- endif -%}

                {%- comment -%} Usage timing {%- endcomment -%}
                <div class="hm-routine-step-card__meta">
                  {%- assign time_of_day = step.best_for_time_of_day | split: '"' | join: '' | remove: '[' | remove: ']' | replace: ',', ' & ' | strip -%}
                  {%- if time_of_day != blank -%}
                    <span class="hm-routine-step-card__meta-item">🕐 {{ time_of_day }}</span>
                  {%- endif -%}
                  {%- if step.absorption_time != blank -%}
                    <span class="hm-routine-step-card__meta-item">⏱ Absorbs in {{ step.absorption_time }}</span>
                  {%- endif -%}
                  {%- if step.texture_type != blank -%}
                    <span class="hm-routine-step-card__meta-item">✦ {{ step.texture_type }}</span>
                  {%- endif -%}
                </div>
              </div>

              {%- comment -%} Shop this step CTA {%- endcomment -%}
              {%- assign step_products = step.active_ingredients -%}
              {%- if step_products and step_products.size > 0 -%}
                <div class="hm-routine-step-card__cta">
                  {%- for prod_ref in step_products limit: 1 -%}
                    {%- assign prod = prod_ref.value -%}
                    {%- if prod.url != blank -%}
                      <a href="{{ prod.url }}" class="hm-routine-step-card__btn">Shop Step {{ step_num }} →</a>
                    {%- endif -%}
                  {%- endfor -%}
                </div>
              {%- endif -%}
            </div>
          {%- endfor -%}
        {%- else -%}
          {%- comment -%} Fallback if no metaobject entries exist yet {%- endcomment -%}
          {%- assign step_names = 'Prep & Cleanse,Treat & Target,Hydrate & Plump,Seal & Protect' | split: ',' -%}
          {%- assign step_desc = 'Double cleanse to remove impurities and prep skin for actives.,Apply targeted serums with active ingredients for your skin concern.,Layer hydrating essences and toners to plump and balance.,Lock in moisture and protect the skin barrier.' | split: ',' -%}
          {%- for i in (1..4) -%}
            <div class="hm-routine-step-card" data-step="{{ i }}">
              <div class="hm-routine-step-card__header">
                <span class="hm-routine-step-card__number">Step {{ i }}</span>
                <h3 class="hm-routine-step-card__name">{{ step_names[forloop.index0] }}</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="hm-routine-step-card__body">
                <p class="hm-routine-step-card__story">{{ step_desc[forloop.index0] }}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          {%- endfor -%}
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ── BUNDLE CTA ── {%- endcomment -%}
  {%- if section.settings.bundle_product != blank -%}
    {%- assign bundle = section.settings.bundle_product -%}
    <section class="hm-routine-bundle">
